MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 562

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE COMPOSTELA CENTRAL ELEMENTARY SCHOOL A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN POBLACION, COMPOSTELA, DAVAO DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO.

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, CORAZON C. AQUINO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale, entry, disposition or settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the Compostela Central Elementary School under the administration of the Department of Education, Culture and Sports, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in Poblacion, Compostela, Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, and more particularly described and bounded as follows:

Lot No. 37-B, Csd-11-010153-D identical to Lot No. 13631, Cad. 282, Compostela Cadastre

(COMPOSTELA CENTRAL ELEMENTARY SCHOOL)

A parcel of land, Lot No. 37-B, Csd-11-010153-D, identical to Lot No. 13631, Cad. 282, Compostela Cadastre situated in Poblacion, Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the NE., along lines 7-8-9 by Road; on the SE., along line 9-1 by Road; along lines 1-2-3-4-5 by Lot 37-A, Csd-11-010153-D identical to Lot 13630, Cad. 282, Compostela Cadastre (Compostela Municipal High School); on the SW., along line 5-6 and NW., along line 6-7 both by Road. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 31 deg. 41′ E., 571.01 m. from BLLM No. 5, Cad. 282, Compostela Cadastre.

124.59 m. to point 2;

80.55 m. to point 3;

152.12 m. to point 4;

86.81 m. to point 5;

275.00 m. to point 6;

358.70 m. to point 7;

300.02 m. to point 8;

290.32 m. to point 9;

170.26 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of ONE HUNDRED FIFTY SEVEN THOUSAND EIGHT HUNDRED AND TWENTY THREE (157,823) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as follows: points 6-7 and 9 are B.L. Cyl. Conc. Mons., 15×60 cm. and the rest are P.S. Cyl. Conc. Mons., 15×40 cm. Bearings true; date of original survey February 2, 1950 to February 29, 1952, that of the subdivision survey on October 12, 1988 by Geodetic Engineer Josefino V. Cacatian and was approved on October 26, 1988.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 3rd day of May , in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) CATALINO MACARAIG, JR. Executive Secretary

